beer.beer_description:
Haze Invicta! 
Hail, humulus lupulus! 
A truly monumentous achievement to last the ages. The freshest bushels of Citra, Trident, and Nectaron hops provide a monolithic flavour to this deceivingly little IPA. 
Big flavour without the booze. 
A true sheep in wolf's clothing. Huzzah!
